name: 3D MVP Lacrosse (iOS/Android videogame) (Canceled)
blurb: Help make a NEW LACROSSE VIDEOGAME for iphones, ipads and Android devices!

rewards.reward: FIRST FAN: You get the finished game on the platform of your choice and your name in the credits for being one of its First Fans!  We'll also give you a downloadable collection of digital artwork featuring high resolution game and concept art!  Thanks for your help! \r\n------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK]

TEAM PLAYER: You get the finished game on the platform of your choice and we'll put *YOU IN THE GAME* by personalizing a player with your name and number! So anytime someone plays the game, it could be with or against YOU! You'll also get the digital artwork collection and be listed in the game's credits as one of our Team Players. You're awesome! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER]

TEAM CAPTAIN: We'll add you as a personalized player and let you *NAME YOUR TEAM* - we'll even let you pick your team colors! Plus you'll get the finished game on the platform of your choice, the digital artwork collection, and we'll put you in the credits as one of our Team Captains! That's great teamwork! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM]

CUSTOM ILLUSTRATION OF YOU (LIMITED): Send us a photo of you in action on the lacrosse field and we\u2019ll create an original piece of concept artwork just like one of the ones here featuring YOU! With this reward you'll get a high resolution digital version of an original custom art piece, plus the finished game on the platform of your choice, the personalized player and team, the digital artwork collection, and your name in the credits as a Supporter of the Lacrosse Arts! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + CUSTOM ART PIECE (DIGITAL)]

ELITE TROPHY CHAMPION (LIMITED): This reward immortalizes your last name forever on one of our in-game trophies! When players think of victory, your name will come to mind! We'll even let you pick the trophy's style and color, plus you'll get the finished game on the platform of your choice, the personalized player and team, the digital artwork collection, and your name in the credits as one of our rare Elite Trophy Champions! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + PERSONALIZED TROPHY]

CUSTOM PAINTING OF YOU (LIMITED): Send us a photo of you playing lacrosse and we\u2019ll create an original piece of custom artwork just like one of these that you can hang on your wall! This is a one-of-a-kind original painting, featuring YOU, created by hand and mailed to your home! You'll also get the finished game on the platform of your choice, the personalized player and team, the digital artwork collection, and your name in the credits as a Supporter of the Lacrosse Arts! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + CUSTOM ART PIECE (PHYSICAL)]

MOTION TALENT SPECIALIST (LIMITED): Do you have some sweet moves? Want to see them in the game? Visit us in Maryland to get motion captured, or send us video of you performing your favorite shot and we'll add it into the game! How awesome is that? You'll also get the finished game on the platform of your choice, the digital artwork collection, the personalized player and team, and get your name in the exclusive Motion Talent section of our credits!  We can't wait to get you in the game! (Any travel expenses are on you, but if you come for a session we'll buy you lunch!) ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + MOTION CAPTURE]

OFFICIAL 3D MVP QUALITY TESTER (LIMITED): In addition to the finished game, you'll get access to early gameplay builds long before anyone else, and will have direct input on the game as it gets developed! You'll be on email threads and conference calls, and will be invited to our beta test conference in Baltimore, Maryland where you can meet and speak with our development team in person (lunch will be provided but any travel expenses are on you, and you must supply your own iOS or Android device). With this reward you'll also get the digital artwork collection, the personalized player and team, and we'll list you in the credits as an official 3D MVP Quality Tester under the Development Team section. We'll also reserve a beta tester spot for you on our future lacrosse games, because you rock! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + EARLY DEVELOPMENT ACCESS + BETA TEST EVENT]

YOUR AD HERE - MATCH SPONSOR (LIMITED): Looking to advertise your company?  We'll add your name to setup screens as a periodic match sponsor before match gameplay begins. Team Captain level rewards are included! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + IN-GAME ADVERTISING (MATCH SPONSOR)]

YOUR AD HERE - EQUIPMENT SPONSOR (LIMITED): How about a whole branded line of lacrosse gear named after your organization? Pick this reward and when players upgrade pieces of stat-enhancing gear they'll be seeing and selecting your name. Team Captain level rewards are included! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + IN-GAME ADVERTISING (PRODUCT BRAND)]

YOUR AD HERE - FIELD SPONSOR (LIMITED): Looking for maximum brand exposure?  With this reward we'll add your logo onto the 3D play field where it will receive high visibility during actual gameplay. Team Captain level rewards are included! ------------------------------------------------------> [GAME + NAME IN CREDITS + DIGITAL ARTWORK + PERSONALIZED PLAYER + PERSONALIZED TEAM + IN-GAME ADVERTISING (ON FIELD)]
